title: Maxon Cinema4d R15 Win+Mac Hybrid ISO
description:
This is another Hybrid Installer for Maxon Cinema4d R15: It Includes all maxon software in the installer though I only include the studio serials its all most should need.

 I have not fully tested this Cinema4d Version yet So im not 100% that every single thing is working as I was in my R14 upload. Though it comes from the same source So I imagine everything Is working.

As before you will need winemu which is the only clean windows iso mounter I know about. Or similar mounting software for mac. This will install on either.
Don't forget whenever you open Cinema4d for the first time you will need to goto edi
